export default [
  {
    id: 1,
    name: "Roll the Dice",
    category: "HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript",
    screenshot: "http://thamer.codefactory.live/images/rollthedice.JPG",
    info:
      "The very beginning of playing around with JavaScript which ended in a very exciting 2 player´s dice game. You can personalize the game with giving names to the players and choose the amount of dices to play with. The board gives out the sum of the dices and tells you who has won or lost or if there is a draw.",
      url: "https://thamer.codefactory.live/dice/index.html",
      github: "https://github.com/manolf/CFLSM-JAVASCRIPT_THAMER_DICE.git"
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: "Travel Agency",
    category: "Angular, HTML5, CSS3, Typescript",
    screenshot: "http://thamer.codefactory.live/images/travel.JPG",
    info:
      "Travel Ageny: This was my first Angular Project. You can browse through the travel offers and choose your trip(s). The selection goes into the shopping cart with a basic webshop functionality. There are implemented TypeScript Functions for the calculation of price, sum and discount",
      url: "https://thamer.codefactory.live/myTravelOffers/",
      github: "https://github.com/manolf/CFLMS-Manuela-CodeReview-07.git"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: "Pet Adoption Site",
    category: "HTML5, CSS3, PHP, MYSQL",
    screenshot: "http://thamer.codefactory.live/images/petshop.jpg",
    info:
      "My first FullStack Project with Login-, Administration System using Crud- and Backend Functionalities. For testing the userrole just do the registerprocess and login to test the userrole. For the admin-access use the credentials admin@gmail.com pw: waldemar. In the administrator panel you can edit, update and delete animal card data. There is also a superadministrator panel to edit User Roles.",
      url: "https://thamer.codefactory.live/animals/index.php",
      github: "https://github.com/manolf/LMSCF-manuela-thamer-petadoption-CR11.git"
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    name: "Autumn of Rock",
    category: "Symfony",
    screenshot: "http://thamer.codefactory.live/images/autumnofrock.JPG",
    info:
      "Here is the example of an Eventsite developed with Symfony 4.3 with the following Functionalities: There is a CRUD-System for adding, updating and deleting event data as well as an eventsFilter for browsing different categories of Rock. Unfortunately the current server does not support this version of Symfony :-( ..",
      url: "https://github.com/manolf/CFLMS-Manuela-Thamer-CodeReview13.git",
      github: "https://github.com/manolf/CFLMS-Manuela-Thamer-CodeReview13.git"
